txt.en: Radagast has many tasks that need completing in the Vales of Anduin.\n\nYou should assist Radagast in the Vales of Anduin.
Radagast has many tasks that need completing in the Vales of Anduin.\n\nYou should assist Radagast in the Vales of Anduin.
'You have done much to aid my efforts.'
Radagast can be found in Rhosgobel.\n\nYou should talk to Radagast.
'You have done much to aid my efforts here in the Vales. Take this as a token of my appreciation.'

Radagast has an additional gift for your troubles in assisting his effort to restore the Vales of Anduin to the peaceful and beautiful place that it once was. Once you have assisted him throughout the Vales, seek out Radagast, and he will reward you for your efforts.
